<div type="definition">
<p>ARTIFICIAL MOUND of MANY THINGS ACCUMULATED in the SAME PLACE.</p></div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The current word for any heap of any material is duī 堆.</p>
<p>2. Dié 垤 refers specifically to an anthill, and then more generally to any small heap of earth.</p></div>
